org.gradoop.dataintegration.transformation.functions

Class EdgesFromLocalTransitiveClosure<V extends EPGMVertex,E extends EPGMEdge>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.dataintegration.transformation.functions.EdgesFromLocalTransitiveClosure<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The vertex type.
    E - The edge type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.CoGroupFunction<org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<V,List<NeighborhoodVertex>>,org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<V,List<NeighborhoodVertex>>,E>, org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.Function, org.apache.flink.api.java.typeutils.ResultTypeQueryable<E>

    public class EdgesFromLocalTransitiveClosure<V extends EPGMVertex,E extends EPGMEdge>
extends Object
implements org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.CoGroupFunction<org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<V,List<NeighborhoodVertex>>,org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<V,List<NeighborhoodVertex>>,E>, org.apache.flink.api.java.typeutils.ResultTypeQueryable<E>
    This function supports the calculation of the transitive closure in the direct neighborhood of a vertex. For each transitive connection an edge is created containing the properties of the central vertex and the labels of the first and second edge that need to be traversed for the transitive connection.
